{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Function.prototype.toSource()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>プロパティ</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/arguments\"><code>Function.prototype.arguments</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/caller\"><code>Function.prototype.caller</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code></a></li></ol></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>メソッド</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><em><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></em></li></ol></li><li><strong>継承</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>プロパティ</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>メソッド</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <div class=\"notecard obsolete\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>廃止:</strong> この機能は廃止されました。まだいくつかのブラウザーで動作するかもしれませんが、いつ削除されてもおかしくないので、使わないようにしましょう。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>toSource()</code></strong> メソッドは、オブジェクトのソースコードを表す文字列を返します。このメソッドは通常、コード中で明示的に呼び出されるのではなく、 JavaScript から内部的に呼び出されます。デバッグ中にオブジェクトの内容を調査する目的で <code>toSource()</code> を呼び出すことができます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>function</var>.toSource();\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>オブジェクトのソースコードを表す文字列です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"解説","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"native_functions","title":"ネイティブ関数","isH3":true,"content":"<p>組込みの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a> オブジェクトでは、 <code>toSource()</code> は次の文字列を返してソースコードが使用できないことを示します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>native code<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"custom_functions","title":"独自の関数","isH3":true,"content":"<p>独自に作成した関数では、 <code>toSource()</code> はオブジェクトを定義する JavaScript のソースコードを文字列として返します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 例:</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">hello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello, World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nhello<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toSource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 結果:</span>\n\"<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">hello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\\\"Hello<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> World<span class=\"token operator\">!</span>\\\"<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\"</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<p>いずれの標準仕様でも定義されていません。</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Function.toSource","dataURL":"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toSource()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"解説","id":"description"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"toSource() メソッドは、オブジェクトのソースコードを表す文字列を返します。このメソッドは通常、コード中で明示的に呼び出されるのではなく、 JavaScript から内部的に呼び出されます。デバッグ中にオブジェクトの内容を調査する目的で toSource() を呼び出すことができます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Function.prototype.toSource()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Function.prototype.toSource()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Function.prototype.toSource()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Function.prototype.toSource()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Function.prototype.toSource()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/function/tostring","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-conten